<topic id="dita-map-transform">
  <title>Transforming DITA Maps and Topics</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>DITA Maps<indexterm>transforming DITA
    Maps</indexterm></indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p><ph keyref="product"/> uses the DITA Open
      Toolkit (DITA-OT) to transform DITA maps and topics into an output format. For this purpose
      both the DITA Open Toolkit <ph
        keyref="ditaOTVersion"/> and ANT 1.7 come
      bundled in <ph keyref="product"/>.</p>
    <p>More information about the DITA Open Toolkit are available at <xref
        href="http://dita-ot.sourceforge.net/" scope="external" format="html"
        >http://dita-ot.sourceforge.net/</xref>.</p>
  </body>
